As a new user to SAP commerce , there is a need to access the backoffice with initial credentials

Environment
SAP Commerce Cloud

Resolution
1.Go to your Commerce Cloud Portal of the specific environment.

2. Here in the bottom you will see the services in that there is a (view All )option Click that.

3.Then you will see the whole list of services and in the bottom somewhere there is hcs_admin Click on that.
4.Then you will see properties click on that.
5. Now you will see on the right hand side there is Initial passwords with the user name "admin" and "anonymous".
6. click on the eye icon you will see  to copy the password of either "admin" and "anonymous and then you can login with that.
